po應該係難玩<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得CM要玩得好先最難，一日到黑全世界追著你提款，做5位又要擠啲眼錢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔買霧捉又被屌鳩，farm一兩jungle出眼都好難<br />\n<br />\n我認我廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf29bd358a4bac6f5abc98768c99b02c564046d","tid":231711,"uid":8794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Invo 你練多幾場就唔難，會戰咪又係吹風隕石音波刀三招做主打，冰冰冰同衛星砲汁下雞咁<br />\n<br />\nMeepo應該係難玩<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得CM要玩得好先最難，一日到黑全世界追著你提款，做5位又要擠啲眼錢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔買霧捉又被屌鳩，farm一兩jungle出眼都好難<br />\n<br />\n我認我廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記唔到招 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢事比人串injoker<br />\n<br />\n反而覺得cm幾易玩 啲技易用又易殺人 gank幾個都有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b8a289204c82be1ec330e03c9fd930ad5592c5","tid":231711,"uid":16210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:09:19.000Z","msg":"公廁 Invoker 開局 都ban左先<br />\n<br />\n利申: 識出招<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6924bbb5bbd2f9c0a95c61f9023d0e7adfbd84","tid":231711,"uid":74237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T20:40:50.000Z","msg":"Meepo"},{"pid":"92ded8a95f5e40cb6962760093e3ff3a112041ab","tid":231711,"uid":16210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T23:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇人回<br />\n由得佢沉"}]}